<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Success</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c63ff, #92a3fd);
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .container {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 450px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            transform: translateY(-20px);
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-50px); }
            100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .container h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #6c63ff;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .container p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #555;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            background: #6c63ff;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #5a55d6;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #777;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #6c63ff;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            color: #5a55d6;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Password Reset Success!</h1>
        <p>We have sent a password reset link to <strong><%= email %></strong>. Please check your inbox (and spam folder) to reset your password.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn">Return to Home</a>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need assistance? <a href="/support">Contact Support</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

